title: Windows 8.1 Pro VL English - MSDN Untouched
description:
Windows 8.1 Pro is built for small and medium sized businesses and delivers new levels of mobility and security, without sacrificing performance or choice, while simplifying technology. Windows 8.1 Pro provides enhanced features that help to easily connect to company networks, use devices as kiosks, encrypt data, and more.

Windows 8.1 Pro N is built for small and medium sized businesses and delivers new levels of mobility and security, without sacrificing performance or choice, while simplifying technology. Windows 8.1 Pro N provides enhanced features that help to easily connect to company networks, use devices as kiosks, encrypt data, and more. Windows 8.1 Pro N includes the same functionality as Windows 8.1 Pro, except that it does not include certain media related technologies (Windows Media Player, Camera, Music, Video).
